Theo Greenly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theo_Greenly 0 Theo Greenly (born March 27, 1985) is an American actor. He is perhaps best known for role as Elliott Rifkin on the Disney Channel series The Jersey. In 1997, he co-starred with Pauly Shore in Shore's self-titled Fox sitcom Pauly. His other television credits include Profiler, Judging Amy and the animated series Fillmore!.His film credits include Jerry Maguire (1996), Touch (1997), Chump Change (2001) and A.I.
